</p><note type="important" id="GUID-753DA41A-EA35-4047-80E0-69F14FCEC358" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p "> Do not lean on the strip support. 
</p></note></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Slide the Curing carriage out of the way toward the middle. 
</p></li></ol></prereq><section id="GUID-E4895B67-7FC1-4974-A5C8-D34725505879" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Required tools</title><ul id="UL_DEE3D96591084F92B951767C25C73502" class="- topic/ul "><li id="LI_5F744141DC964DB091AE77E6BD3956DE" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Screwdriver Torx T20. 
</p></li><li id="LI_929C0F12811B4096BB70DA320BD9C6C8" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Protective gloves : 
<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Microflex 
</b> 93-260 gloves. 
</p></li></ul></section><section id="GUID-C02D66D1-E3CC-4BC2-95F8-775D93D93431" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Warning / Caution</title><note type="caution" id="GUID-A97040BC-F110-4E4B-9CFF-E8082B9DA00E" class="- topic/note "><fig id="GUID-2D7D94A0-B26C-4C0B-B6A3-20C8621663A2" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-FCF86E23-0DD4-40BC-ACDF-FF8ABA1E6502-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-FCF86E23-0DD4-40BC-ACDF-FF8ABA1E6502-low.png"/></fig><p class="- topic/p ">Avoid skin contact with ink: wear protective gloves. 
</p><fig id="GUID-7C716739-2AD7-42F8-8EF6-B28A8E7B1F76" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-D8099BBE-C3A2-4392-8B56-C532EDDD6073-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-D8099BBE-C3A2-4392-8B56-C532EDDD6073-low.png"/></fig><p class="- topic/p "> Protect your eyes from splashing ink: wear safety glasses. 
</p></note></section><section id="GUID-EC9C24D5-D455-4022-B616-D7FEF4DE0A1A" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Illustration</title><fig id="FIG_3C5C54183244495883538CAB573C6EEE" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-33E1729A-37D1-46C5-AA77-7E2B80EBF731-low.png" id="IMAGE_1D754147ADD347B29314B124350B935C" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-33E1729A-37D1-46C5-AA77-7E2B80EBF731-low.png"/></fig></section><section id="SECTION_9B52B4F9A6064E8FA0DA985640631979" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">How to install</title><table pgwide="1" id="TABLE_72520E2720514D4A9F47D90E3DC56450" class="- topic/table "><tgroup align="left" outputclass="step" cols="3" class="- topic/tgroup "><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="10*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="50*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col3" colnum="3" colwidth="40*" class="- topic/colspec "/><thead valign="top" class="- topic/thead "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Step 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remarks 
</p></entry></row></thead><tbody valign="top" class="- topic/tbody "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">1 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the 2 locking strips (4 screws). 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-E03AC0F6-DD09-448C-B109-A0E0A685FF40" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-FEEAA24A-7286-485F-8709-E30BD0B32384-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-FEEAA24A-7286-485F-8709-E30BD0B32384-low.png"/></fig><fig id="FIG_C0C2895333C34624870BBA33FB962F78" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-E43A6D01-6C56-4332-8A09-970A191864F3-low.png" id="IMAGE_86A5DDD84C9142BEB41ADC0FD0C4FEF1" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-E43A6D01-6C56-4332-8A09-970A191864F3-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">2 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the 2 assemblies. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-EEA33316-7385-44ED-94D9-AA814DC4A193" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-F333A944-B980-4979-8B53-E607CF2CCD29-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-F333A944-B980-4979-8B53-E607CF2CCD29-low.png"/></fig><fig id="FIG_B5BF4770BD6946E791BEC4C2DAE025B8" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-C0554771-E915-49B6-8FDC-DA3956DAB6BE-low.png" id="IMAGE_5DB218C87A874A788B8AF2D53BDC47AA" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-C0554771-E915-49B6-8FDC-DA3956DAB6BE-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">3 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Place the filter on the assembly (2x). 
</p><note type="important" id="GUID-6BEC1E24-EDF5-426E-918E-D566F90668ED" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p ">Check the airflow direction: 
</p><ul class="- topic/ul "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">foam strips on the filter should be at the bottom side 
</p></li></ul></note></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="FIG_88DFBA49736C4A25B07158698D3B4663" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-6EF08FB3-5267-41A2-AC6A-3FFD61434A0A-low.png" id="IMAGE_6E7D58F1828243ECBF707A57908FD7C2" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-6EF08FB3-5267-41A2-AC6A-3FFD61434A0A-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">4 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Install the 2 filters in the printer. 
</p><note type="important" id="GUID-0086850E-BB97-4146-B28E-6A277F1C768A" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p ">Lower handle at the right hand side. 
</p></note></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-DE853A73-FD5A-4773-9808-1312DBF19F50" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-FB0C1E99-63E4-4036-A8F6-F911B4212515-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-FB0C1E99-63E4-4036-A8F6-F911B4212515-low.png"/></fig><fig id="FIG_1FFA0226F52340FEB3B7C53375D36824" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-33E1729A-37D1-46C5-AA77-7E2B80EBF731-low.png" id="IMAGE_3AEFC5D0056F4F63B4F917E540291C43" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-33E1729A-37D1-46C5-AA77-7E2B80EBF731-low.png"/></fig></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></section></taskbody><related-links class="- topic/related-links "><linkpool class="- topic/linkpool " mapkeyref="GUID-8A41CFEA-5928-4042-A2CB-507A5D034160"><link class="- topic/link " mapclass="- map/topicref " format="dita" type="concept" href="generated-topic-GUID-64346CA7-1EE0-4BCD-B397-069F12247FBC.xml" role="parent"><?ditaot usertext?><linktext class="- topic/linktext "><?ditaot usertext?>Installation</linktext></link></linkpool></related-links>
